<p>
  <span class="nym">Amant</span>
  <span class="gen">m.</span>
  
  <span class="etym"><span class="lang">Latin</span> <i>amandus</i> 'meant to be loved'.
  </span>
  
</p>
  
<div class="usg">
  <p>The name of a 7th C French saint.</p>
</div>
  
  


